---
import StarlightPage from '@astrojs/starlight/components/StarlightPage.astro';
---

<StarlightPage frontmatter={{ title: 'About', template: 'splash', hero: { tagline: '' } }}>
  <div class="about-page">
    <section class="about-header">
      <h1>About RTMX</h1>
      <p class="about-subtitle">
        The people and principles behind the intent layer for agentic engineering.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Company</h2>
      <p>
        RTMX is built by <strong>ioTACTICAL LLC</strong>, an engineering company focused on
        developer tools for AI-driven development and regulated industries. We build software
        that helps teams maintain engineering discipline as they adopt agentic workflows.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Founder</h2>
      <div class="founder-card">
        <div class="founder-info">
          <h3>Ryan McLean</h3>
          <p>
            Ryan's background spans federal engineering and defense software, including work on
            <strong>TAK.gov</strong> (Android Tactical Assault Kit) — the U.S. military's
            situational awareness platform. That experience building mission-critical software
            under strict traceability requirements shaped the design philosophy behind RTMX.
          </p>
          <p>
            Now he's building tools for agentic engineering — giving development teams the
            infrastructure to keep AI agents accountable to human intent.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section mission-section">
      <h2>Mission</h2>
      <blockquote class="mission-quote">
        "We believe the shift to AI-driven development needs better engineering discipline, not
        less. RTMX exists to make AI agents accountable to human intent."
      </blockquote>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Open Source</h2>
      <p>
        RTMX is licensed under <strong>Apache 2.0</strong> and built in public. Our
        requirements traceability matrix is managed by RTMX itself — we use the tool to build
        the tool. You can follow our progress on the
        <a href="/roadmap">Roadmap</a> or browse the source on
        <a href="https://github.com/rtmx-ai/rtmx-go">GitHub</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-section">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <div class="contact-grid not-content">
        <div class="contact-item">
          <h3>Technical</h3>
          <a href="mailto:dev@rtmx.ai">dev@rtmx.ai</a>
          <p>Engineering questions, bug reports, and integrations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-item">
          <h3>Enterprise</h3>
          <a href="mailto:sales@rtmx.ai">sales@rtmx.ai</a>
          <p>On-prem deployment, compliance, and volume licensing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-item">
          <h3>Support</h3>
          <a href="mailto:help@rtmx.ai">help@rtmx.ai</a>
          <p>General help, account issues, and documentation feedback.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="about-footer">
      <nav class="footer-community" aria-label="Community links">
        <a href="https://github.com/rtmx-ai/rtmx-go/discussions" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub Discussions</a>
        <span class="footer-sep" aria-hidden="true">/</span>
        <a href="https://github.com/rtmx-ai/rtmx-go/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub Issues</a>
        <span class="footer-sep" aria-hidden="true">/</span>
        <a href="mailto:dev@rtmx.ai">dev@rtmx.ai</a>
      </nav>
    </footer>
  </div>
</StarlightPage>

<style is:global>
  /* Hide Starlight's default hero/title for about page */
  .hero,
  main > header,
  .content-panel > header,
  [aria-label="Main"] > header {
    display: none !important;
  }

  .main-pane,
  .content-panel {
    padding: 0 !important;
    padding-block: 0 !important;
  }

  .sl-container {
    max-width: 100% !important;
    padding: 0 !important;
  }

  main {
    padding: 0 !important;
  }

  .about-page {
    background: #0a0a0a;
    min-height: 100vh;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .about-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 2rem 2rem;
  }

  .about-header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #6ee7b7 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .about-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #9ca3af;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .about-section {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 2rem 0;
  }

  .about-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f9fafb;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .about-section p {
    color: #9ca3af;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .about-section strong {
    color: #e5e7eb;
  }

  .about-section a {
    color: #10b981;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .about-section a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .founder-card {
    background: #171717;
    border: 1px solid #262626;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .founder-info h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #f9fafb;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .founder-info p {
    color: #9ca3af;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .founder-info p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .mission-quote {
    background: #171717;
    border-left: 3px solid #10b981;
    border-radius: 0 0.5rem 0.5rem 0;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #d1d5db;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .contact-section {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 2rem 3rem;
  }

  .contact-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f9fafb;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contact-item {
    background: #171717;
    border: 1px solid #262626;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }

  .contact-item h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #f9fafb;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .contact-item a {
    color: #10b981;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .contact-item a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .contact-item p {
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0 0;
  }

  .about-footer {
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid #262626;
  }

  .about-footer p {
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-footer a {
    color: #10b981;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .about-footer a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .about-footer .footer-community {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .about-footer .footer-community a {
    color: #10b981;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .about-footer .footer-community a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .about-footer .footer-sep {
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .about-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
    }

    .about-subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .contact-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
